title: Prep volleyball: Simpson helps pace Faith Christian to eighth win in nine matches
text:
Photo by Bill Wilson / The Anniston Star High school volleyball 
Photo by Bill Wilson / The Anniston Star Posted: Thursday, October 1, 2015 9:36 pm | Updated: 9:41 pm, Thu Oct 1, 2015. Prep volleyball: Simpson helps pace Faith Christian to eighth win in nine matches Star staff Annistonstar.com 
The Faith Christian volleyball Lions scored two wins Thursday to give them eight wins in their last nine matches. 
Faith Christian beat Moody 25-6, 25-18 and Munford 25-19, 25-23 as Cornelia Simpson produced an all-around game of five aces, six blocks, 10 kills and 15 digs. Subscription Required An online service is needed to view this article in its entirety. You
